<title>HONG KONG: Pacific Concord up on spinoff hopes.</title>
<headline>Pacific Concord up on spinoff hopes.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-10-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Shares of watch maker and distributor Pacific Concord Holdings Ltd surged to hit a year high on hopes of a possible spinoff, brokers said on Thursday.</p>
<p>Its shares rose HK$0.175 or 8.75 percent to HK$2.175 at midday on volume of 27.11 million shares worth HK$57.31 million.</p>
<p>&quot;Renewed speculation of an exceptional gain from a spinoff boosted demand, especially as a spin off is expected to take place very soon,&quot; said a research manager at a local brokerage.</p>
